{"id": "1511387191044214854", "channel_id": "1511380800606703786", "type": 0, "author_id": "819349396789526619", "author_name": "tajimal_drawing", "author_bot": false, "content": "オレッタさん　かなり偉いスキル構成してると思うんだけど　どうなんでしょうね\n腺体分裂0コスやし引いたら山札に入るし狂気解放でその数分殴るし", "timestamp": "2026-06-02T15:13:06.561000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1511380800606703786", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸々の備忘録", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1511351358052241518", "channel_id": "1510911214346305566", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢ミリアムステージ\n\n以前ミリアムにボコられ過ぎてトラウマになっているため、あえて雑魚戦を一つ増やして挑んでしまう。\nが、やっぱり以前よりミリアム弱体化されてるのか、普通に勝ててしまう。直行すれば良かった。\nライカーのダメデカ過ぎて毒パ失格なダメージバランス。\n\nとりあえず8640点。明日から沙耶試そうかな。", "timestamp": "2026-06-02T12:50:43.310000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-02T12:53:50.358000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1511351356915449906", "filename": "IMG_8231.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 597484, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511351356915449906/IMG_8231.png?ex=6a33e9a3&is=6a329823&hm=e04eafebd024c37fcb2a7177508352ae0941105e6459538391e4e1b1a937ce7b&"}, {"id": "1511351357708304505", "filename": "IMG_8230.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 367249, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511351357708304505/IMG_8230.png?ex=6a33e9a3&is=6a329823&hm=2e5dcf35157486bd1277b210a90adbfaa8ab4e46de8ace007d9830e5c9821ca4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510911214346305566", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "ニムフィーアの毒パ研究日誌", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1511387602740314317", "channel_id": "1510911214346305566", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "ライムさんに教えてもらったリッツ毒パの試用運転。\n沙耶イベスト高難度。\nオルラ→タイス→リッツのシナジーが強過ぎて毒発動する前に即死。\n次ターンアグで毒誘発✖️2で20,000弱ダメージでニヤリとする予定だったのに…。\nシンプルにもっと体力ある敵や堅固でガチガチな敵、何度も形態変化する相手とかなら毒パっぽい戦いができるかも？", "timestamp": "2026-06-02T15:14:44.717000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-02T23:00:03.379000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1511387602064900218", "filename": "IMG_8241.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 715701, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511387602064900218/IMG_8241.png?ex=6a340b64&is=6a32b9e4&hm=76b6b6dd100e2ddca695f0c3819f7521f8cbe271731158ca7b995ee91e82a429&"}, {"id": "1511387602471883013", "filename": "IMG_8236.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 443558, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511387602471883013/IMG_8236.png?ex=6a340b64&is=6a32b9e4&hm=df5a89033ffb6a53c2ec1d7e3c7602344e74832a59c84240fb86821afe19b108&"}, {"id": "1511387602840719502", "filename": "IMG_8237.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 435310, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511387602840719502/IMG_8237.png?ex=6a340b64&is=6a32b9e4&hm=1174ac1bcc5a3e636442256d13d3dedf8dadadcc9c192419aef820833338d860&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510911214346305566", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "ニムフィーアの毒パ研究日誌", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
